OL,7,FNorth Wales Fire and Rescue Service
OL,8,Fhas had its White Ribbon accreditation
OL,9,Fsuspended.
OL,11,FThe charity White Ribbon UK has today
OL,12,Fpublished a statement on its website
OL,13,Ffollowing concerns about the culture
OL,14,Fat North Wales Fire and Rescue Service.
OL,16,FIt says: "We have suspended North
OL,17,FWales Fire and Rescue Service's
OL,18,FAccreditation."
