OL,7,FNorth Wales Fire and Rescue Service
OL,8,Fwas awarded White Ribbon accreditation
OL,9,Fin 2019 in recognition of the actions
OL,10,Fit had taken to help end male violence
OL,11,Fagainst women.
OL,13,FAccredited organisations commit to
OL,14,Fworking towards ending harmful
OL,15,Fcultures that lead to violence, with
OL,16,Fan action plan.
OL,18,FWhite Ribbon UK's online statement
OL,19,Fcontinued: "Women's experiences inform
OL,20,Fand drive White Ribbon's work to end
OL,21,Fgender-based violence.
