OL,7,F"White Ribbon UK exists to end
OL,8,Fproblematic, abusive and misogynistic
OL,9,Fmale cultures to stop violence against
OL,10,Fwomen before it starts.
OL,12,F"Our approach is to positively
OL,13,Ftransform harmful attitudes and
OL,14,Fpromote a culture where men understand
OL,15,Fnot to use violence, excuse violence
OL,16,For remain silent about violence ` in
OL,17,Fall its forms."
