OL,7,FNorth Wales Fire and Rescue Service
OL,8,Fsaid it was "disappointing" that White
OL,9,FRibbon UK had chosen to suspend its
OL,10,Faccreditation and it would be looking
OL,11,Fto work with the organisation to
OL,12,Fdiscuss its concerns."
OL,14,FThe service was today asked if they
OL,15,Fwould welcome a Wales-wide review into
OL,16,Fthe culture of fire services.
