OL,7,FIn a statement, North Wales Fire and
OL,8,FRescue Service said it welcomes
OL,9,Freviews into a variety of areas within
OL,10,Fthe service, and they conduct a staff
OL,11,Fsurvey every two years which includes
OL,12,Fquestions on workplace culture, the
OL,13,Flast being conducted in 2023, to
OL,14,Fidentify opportunities for improvement.
