OL,7,FThe statement added: "Furthermore, in
OL,8,FNorth Wales, we fully recognise the
OL,9,Fimplications of the South Wales
OL,10,FCulture Review report and have
OL,11,Facknowledged that it offers valuable
OL,12,Flessons for other fire and rescue
OL,13,Fservices and the public sector as a
OL,14,Fwhole.
OL,16,F"We have taken on board the
OL,17,Frecommendations as a result of the
OL,18,Freview in South Wales, with a thorough
OL,19,Fgap analysis against the report
OL,20,Frecommendations."
