OL,8,Fsay they continually strive to achieve
OL,9,Fthe best culture within the
OL,10,Forganisation and have robust policies,
OL,11,Fprocedures and guidance in place that
OL,12,Fsupport them in achieving the highest
OL,13,Fpossible standards expected by the
OL,14,Fpublic.
OL,16,FIt added: "We recognise that no fire
OL,17,Fand rescue service or indeed any
OL,18,Fpublic service can afford to be
OL,19,Fcomplacent, and there remains room for
OL,20,Fimprovement for us all."
